  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "「コナミGBコレクション Vol. 2」の続編である本作には、アーケードスタイルのタイトルが4つ収録されています：\n\nバイカーズ  \nグッタンゴットゥン  \nミスティカル忍者  \nポップンツインビー",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "The Konami GB Collection is a series of video game compilations for the Game Boy Color. The compilations were originally released from 1997 to 1998 in Japan for Game Boy, and were later released in Europe in 2000 for Game Boy Color.\n\nIncluded in Volume 3:\n- Pop n' TwinBee\n- Mystical Ninja Starring Goemon\n- Bikers (Motocross Maniacs)\n- Guttang Gottong\n\nThis was released as Volume 2 in Japan.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Konami GB Collection is a series of four video game compilations published by Konami, each comprising four of their previously released Game Boy titles on a single cartridge. The compilations were originally released from 1997 to 1998 in Japan on the Game Boy, and featured Super Game Boy palette and border support, with game descriptions and instructions provided by the girls from the original Tokimeki Memorial. The compilations later received a European release in 2000 for the Game Boy Color, which removed the Super Game Boy support and Tokimeki Memorial content but added colour support.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    }
  ],
